        <section id="fs-id2727498" class="short-answer" type="short-answer">
            <title>Short Answer</title>
            <exercise id="fs-id1931824" type="short-answer">
                <problem id="fs-id1748882"> 
                    <para id="import-auto-id1309652">Discuss the differences between a mass and a crowd. What is an example of each? What sets them apart? What do they share in common?</para>
                </problem>
