            <exercise id="fs-id1805613" type="short-answer">
                <problem id="fs-id3613495">
                    <para id="import-auto-id1899781">Can you think of a time when your behavior in a crowd was dictated by the circumstances? Give an example of emergent-norm perspective, using your own experience.</para>
                </problem>
            </exercise>
